"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112117QYyTBI0W594Gj1Dv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711241121271UjH23pNdJySLRG9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711241121190eZ1SK3fQ5hO7JkI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112123tl0EAoJN62QWyd49.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112127aOXc2Cyflm4Qp3nW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112131rptWAREunf6L3iSY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112123fPJMzH2WDnuCIU9Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112126wB4U9xjYJhuvOazQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112126S9tycEpKmOBxlQgd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112134lDZyW5I1iFkCHNmQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112134OJhmVIiEnoLHeZ0k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112135qZWJoaNjGAlwnHh8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112137fojcWqTYMnNAuarV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112137uDykWKON0B3lLtG4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112138FkfKJh396Qbsqv5g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112141jYHAsWynKSNuTxwa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112140S72F0AHJ13xVpNPo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711241121412yi9pmClS5bEgzKV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112313HP2B1IGeAz0fFZE7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112313Yjmu1bC0ZdxylEft.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112313uBQyi4qtlOKJecYg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>来副<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/super-andy-warhol-glasses/\" rel=\"nofollow\">安迪·沃霍尔眼镜</a>？ </p><p>安迪·沃霍尔基金会与 SUPER 合作发布了一款以安迪·沃霍尔的画作为灵感的眼镜，还挺好玩的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112350ogtDwvQJElGyeMIC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112350VNwS0WrRghBYnMb4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112350VtpMAvuIqibXkczW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017112411235413wbKeiCksWjxpYU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112354uocwmVL2NgMIeTYk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>这个月 30 号至 12 月 17 日，Balenciaga 将在伦敦的 Dover Street Market 开设一家快闪店<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/balenciaga-triple-s-price-release-date-info/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Balenciaga Copyshop</a>，现场将会有台印刷设备，可以自己 DIY T 恤。 </p><p>另外，大热的老爸鞋 Triple S 将推出一个 Dover Street Market 限定版本，售价 795 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112408areRxP01kwgsYIQ5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112409DZn9jwRHOi3NBLb7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562121\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Puma 的新代言人 <a href=\"http://footwearnews.com/2017/focus/athletic-outdoor/selena-gomez-debuts-puma-most-functional-fashion-trainer-shoes-yet-459653/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Serena Gomez </a>拍摄了一组新的广告。片中，“国美”穿的这双鞋子号称是 Puma 最具功能性和时尚感的鞋子，它还有粉色和橄榄绿色款，售价 90 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112426Pvy1gcw5psKFie6o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112422pTFg50DIKb9WNkBG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112422wVlaE1xdADWt8yrB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112423v6sqUZxaVc5LTG2i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>GU 和先锋艺术家 Aerosyn-Lex Mestrovic 合作，推出联名系列<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-11-22/gu-aerosyn-lex-mestrovic/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> HYBRID TOKYO</a>，该系列的第一波单品将于 12 月 11 日登陆日本各大 GU 门店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112628DQcnyB5sdUaX6vm8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.437879\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112627bWj85AIp3y2V9Uqk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.313199\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112627vexpET5r73tQwfzN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.079696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711241126271ScNwzLdpTKxeo89.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.290672\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112628AePmDx1SR6ucpwMf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.054104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171124112628l9yU0mj38SgaoN1u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.206651\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>我们之前报道过的三方联名款球鞋 Chanel X Pharrell Williams X Adidas Originals NMD Hu Chanel，可能是今年最受关注的一款鞋了。</p><p>据 wwd 报道，这双售价达 1000 欧元的鞋子，在转售市场很有可能炒到 4 万美元。据这双鞋的指定发售店铺 Colette 介绍，大约有 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/street-style/chanel-pharrell-williams-adidas-sneaker-justin-timberlake-11055165/?curator=FashionREDEF\" rel=\"nofollow\">12 万人</a>在 chanelatcolette.fr 活动官网预约注册，求购这双鞋。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201711241126493drtgK2woIRHTX7N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：佳得乐</p>"}